item.title: Andrew Young - In The Zone (Progressive House)
item.dc:creator: Jax
item.description:
I really like the vibe of this song, nice job! The only feedback I have is that at some parts, the bass sounded like it was playing chords. If they were, you might want to change it to just the base note. But other than that, it sounded spot on. Keep up the good work!
